          <hr class="section-break" />
          <h2 class="heading-level-2" id="5-产品架构-5">5. 产品架构</h2>
          <h3 class="heading-level-3" id="51-客户数字孪生的架构">5.1 客户数字孪生的架构</h3>
          <figure class="diagram-card">
            <figcaption class="diagram-caption"><span class="caption-badge">图示 14</span><span>架构 / 流程图</span>
            </figcaption>
