          <h3 class="heading-level-3" id="41-customermemory-对象模型">4.1 CustomerMemory 对象模型</h3>
          <figure class="code-card">
            <figcaption class="code-caption"><span class="caption-badge">YAML</span></figcaption>
            <pre class="code-pre"><code class="language-yaml">对象名称: CustomerMemory
业务目标: 存储带有上下文、权重和时序的客户交互记忆

核心字段:
  id: UUID (主键)
  customer_id: UUID (关联 Customer)
  created_by: string (来源：Agent / 人工 / 系统)
  
  # 核心内容
  type: enum (
    observation |       # 观察：客户说了什么/做了什么
    interaction |      # 互动：双向交流
    inference |        # 推断：系统的判断
    summary |          # 摘要：对一段时期的总结
    event              # 事件：关键事件记录
  )
  content: text (记忆的原始内容)
  summary: text (AI 自动生成的摘要)
  embedding: vector (语义嵌入向量)
  
  # 时序与权重
  timestamp: datetime (事件发生时间)
  recorded_at: datetime (记录时间)
  importance: float (0.0-1.0，重要性评分)
  confidence: float (0.0-1.0，推断型记忆的置信度)
  
  # 分类
  topic: string[] (话题标签，如["价格", "竞品B", "交期"])
  sentiment: enum (positive | neutral | negative | mixed)
  
  # 关联
  related_entities: map (关联的实体，如{product_id, contact_id, deal_id})
  previous_memory: UUID (关联的上一条相关记忆)
  
  # 合规
  data_source: string (数据来源渠道)
  privacy_level: enum (public | internal | restricted | confidential)
  source_language: string (原始语言)

状态机:
  draft (AI生成，待确认) → active (可被检索)
  active → archived (已归档)
  active → flagged (有问题的记忆，待人工审核)
</code></pre>
