          <h2 class="heading-level-2" id="4-下一代方案-11">4. 下一代方案</h2>
          <h3 class="heading-level-3" id="41-agent-权限模型扩展-rbac">4.1 Agent 权限模型（扩展 RBAC）</h3>
          <figure class="code-card">
            <figcaption class="code-caption"><span class="caption-badge">YAML</span></figcaption>
            <pre class="code-pre"><code class="language-yaml">对象名称: AgentRole
业务目标: 定义 Agent 的权限边界

核心字段:
  id: UUID
  name: string (如 "Sales_L2")
  
  # 数据访问范围
  data_access:
    entity_types: string[] (可访问的对象类型，如["Customer", "Memory", "IntentSignal"])
    data_scope: enum (
      assigned_only |       # 只读分配给它的
      team_visible |        # 可以读团队可见的
      org_visible            # 可以读组织级的
    )
    field_level_restrictions: map (字段级别的限制)
      example: {"Customer.revenue": "read_only", "Contact.phone": "no_access"}
  
  # 操作权限
  allowed_operations: string[] (允许的操作列表)
    - "customer.read"
    - "memory.create"
    - "memory.read"
    - "intent_signal.read"
    - "pipeline.advance_stage" (在授权范围内)
  
  restricted_operations: string[] (禁止的操作列表)
    - "customer.delete"
    - "opportunity.create"
    - "quote.create"
    - "contract.sign"
  
  # 限制条件
  limits:
    max_actions_per_day: int (日操作上限)
    max_actions_per_customer: int (单客户日操作上限)
    min_confidence_for_autonomous: float (自主决策的最低置信度, 如0.7)
    human_confirmation_required: string[] (需要人确认的操作)
      - "pipeline.advance_to_negotiation" (推进到谈判阶段需确认)
      - "memory.flag_as_important" (标记记忆为重要需确认)
  
  # 升级路径
  escalation:
    auto_escalate_on: string[] (自动升级的场景)
    escalation_agent_id: UUID (升级到的另一个Agent)
    escalation_user_id: UUID (升级到的人)
</code></pre>
          </figure>
          <h3 class="heading-level-3" id="42-agent-任务系统">4.2 Agent 任务系统</h3>
          <figure class="code-card">
            <figcaption class="code-caption"><span class="caption-badge">YAML</span></figcaption>
            <pre class="code-pre"><code class="language-yaml">对象名称: AgentTask
业务目标: 管理 Agent 执行的任务单元

核心字段:
  id: UUID
  agent_id: UUID (执行此任务的 Agent)
  customer_id: UUID (关联的客户)
  
  # 任务定义
  task_type: enum (
    outreach |            # 外呼
    follow_up |           # 跟进
    qualification |       # 线索评估
    proposal |            # 报价
    health_check |        # 健康度巡检t
    intervention |        # 干预行动
    analysis              # 数据分析
  )
  status: enum (
    created |             # 已创建，待分配
    assigned |            # 已分配到 Agent
    in_progress |         # 执行中
    awaiting_confirmation |  # 等待人确认
    completed |           # 已完成
    failed |              # 执行失败
    escalated             # 已升级到人处理
  )
  
  # 任务内容
  input: object (任务的输入参数)
  output: object (任务的输出结果)
  reasoning: text (Agent 执行过程中的推理过程，用于审计)
  
  # 触发方式
  trigger_type: enum (
    scheduled |           # 定时触发
    event_driven |        # 事件触发
    manual |              # 人工创建
    agent_initiated       # Agent 主动创建
  )
  trigger_details: object
  
  # 时效
  created_at: datetime
  started_at: datetime
  completed_at: datetime
  priority: enum (low | medium | high | critical)
  
  # 负责人
  created_by: string (Agent 或人)
  supervisor: string (监督人，如有)
  escalated_to: UUID (升级到的人或Agent)

状态机:
  created → assigned → in_progress → awaiting_confirmation → completed
                                      → failed → retry/escalated
           → cancelled
</code></pre>
