          <h3 class="heading-level-3" id="42-mcp-server-配置示例">4.2 MCP Server 配置示例</h3>
          <figure class="code-card">
            <figcaption class="code-caption"><span class="caption-badge">YAML</span></figcaption>
            <pre class="code-pre"><code class="language-yaml"># crm-mcp-server-config.yaml

server_name: "crm4-mcp-server"
server_version: "1.0.0"

# 协议传输方式
transport:
  type: "sse"                       # Server-Sent Events（远程）
  port: 8080
  # type: "stdio"                   # 标准输入输出（本地）
  
# 认证
authentication:
  type: "api_key"
  api_key_header: "X-API-Key"
  
# 工具注册
tools:
  # 1. 客户查询
  - name: "get_customer_context"
    description: "获取客户的当前状态、关键记忆和健康度评分"
    input:
      customer_id:
        type: "string"
        description: "CRM 中的客户 ID 或名称"
        required: true
    output:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        status: { type: "string" }
        key_memories: { type: "array", items: { type: "object" } }
        intent_signals: { type: "array" }
        health_score: { type: "object" }
    handler: "handlers.customer.get_context"
    
  # 2. 记忆写入
  - name: "remember_customer"
    description: "将一条客户记忆写入 CRM 的客户记忆引擎"
    input:
      customer_id:
        type: "string"
        required: true
      content:
        type: "string"
        description: "记忆内容"
        required: true
      importance:
        type: "number"
        description: "重要性 0-1"
        default: 0.5
      tags:
        type: "array"
        items: { type: "string" }
        optional: true
    output:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        memory_id: { type: "string" }
        status: { type: "string" }
    handler: "handlers.memory.write"
    
  # 3. 管道推进
  - name: "advance_pipeline"
    description: "推进或修改机会的管道阶段"
    input:
      opportunity_id:
        type: "string"
        required: true
      target_stage:
        type: "string"
        description: "目标阶段名称"
        required: true
      reasoning:
        type: "string"
        description: "推进此阶段的推理过程"
        optional: true
    output:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        success: { type: "boolean" }
        new_stage: { type: "string" }
        message: { type: "string" }
    handler: "handlers.pipeline.advance"
    permissions:
      require_human_for: ["closed_won", "closed_lost"]
      
  # 4. 关系查询
  - name: "find_relationship"
    description: "查询公司/联系人之间的关系路径"
    input:
      source_type: { type: "string", enum: ["contact", "organization"] }
      source_id: { type: "string" }
      target_type: { type: "string" }
      target_id: { type: "string" }
      max_depth: { type: "integer", default: 3 }
    output:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        paths: { type: "array" }
    handler: "handlers.relationship.find_path"

# 资源注册
resources:
  - uri: "crm://customers/{id}"
    name: "客户基本信息"
    mime_type: "application/json"
    handler: "resources.customer.get"
    
  - uri: "crm://customers/{id}/memories"
    name: "客户记忆列表"
    mime_type: "application/json"
    handler: "resources.memory.list"
    
  - uri: "crm://customers/{id}/health"
    name: "客户健康度"
    mime_type: "application/json"
    handler: "resources.health.get"
</code></pre>
          </figure>
          <h3 class="heading-level-3" id="43-已有-crm-系统的-mcp-桥接">4.3 已有 CRM 系统的 MCP 桥接</h3>
          <p>如果企业已经部署了传统 CRM（Salesforce、纷享销客等），不需要替换——只需要部署一个 MCP 桥接器：</p>
          <figure class="diagram-card">
            <figcaption class="diagram-caption"><span class="caption-badge">图示 190</span><span>架构 / 流程图</span>
            </figcaption>
            <pre class="diagram-pre"><code>┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  MCP Bridge (MQP - Middleware for CRM)        │
│                                                │
│  MCP Client Agent                              │
│     ↓                                          │
│  MCP 路由（协议转译）                           │
│     ↓                                          │
│  REST/SOAP API 适配层                          │
│     ├── Salesforce API Adapter                  │
│     ├── 纷享销客 API Adapter                    │
│     ├── HubSpot API Adapter                     │
│     └── 自定义 API Adapter                      │
│     ↓                                          │
│  传统 CRM                                      │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
</code></pre>
          </figure>
          <p>桥接器的作用：</p>
          <ul>
            <li>将 MCP 协议转译为传统 CRM 的 REST/SOAP API 调用</li>
            <li>保持会话上下文</li>
            <li>将结果格式化为 MCP 格式返回</li>
            <li>处理传统 CRM 的错误码和限流</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>让任何一个 CRM 系统都能接入 MCP 生态——不需要重写 CRM，不需要换系统。</strong></p>
          <h3 class="heading-level-3" id="44-mcp-认证与安全">4.4 MCP 认证与安全</h3>
          <figure class="code-card">
            <figcaption class="code-caption"><span class="caption-badge">YAML</span></figcaption>
            <pre class="code-pre"><code class="language-yaml"># MCP Server 安全配置

security:
  # Agent 身份认证
  authentication:
    providers:
      - type: "api_key"
        key_header: "X-API-Key"
        key_store: "environment_variable"
        
      - type: "jwt"
        jwks_endpoint: "https://auth.company.com/.well-known/jwks.json"
  
  # 权限检查（每个工具调用前）
  authorization:
    default_policy: "deny"      # 默认拒绝
    policies:
      - tool: "get_customer_context"
        allow: "all_agents"     # 所有Agent可以读取
      - tool: "write_memory"
        allow: "authenticated_agents"  # 认证Agent可以写入
      - tool: "advance_pipeline"
        allow: "authorized_agents_only"
        require_scope: "pipeline:write"
  
  # 审计日志
  audit:
    enabled: true
    log_all_calls: true
    log_all_errors: true
    retention_days: 365
    
  # 频控
  rate_limiting:
    default: "100/min"
    per_agent_overrides: {
      "agent-official": "1000/min",
      "agent-third-party": "50/min"
    }
</code></pre>
          </figure>
